BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Rust-AICollective|Responsible AI and Data Protection: Aligning Gha
 na’s Data Protection Act with Emerging AI Use Cases|Online
DTSTART:20260430T153000Z
CATEGORIES:ai,data
DESCRIPTION:Get up-to-date information at: https://luma.com/aidatagh\n\nHo
 sted by The AI Collective\, Knowledge Innovations & Gen Ai Collective Ghan
 a
LOCATION:https://luma.com/event/evt-rI9mxNqygqodV1R
